Package: ablestack-n2k
Version: ${VERSION}-${RELEASE}
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, jq, curl, qemu-utils, libvirt-clients
Maintainer: ABLECLOUD <dev@ablecloud.io>
Description: ABLESTACK Nutanix AHV-to-KVM migration tool
 ablestack_n2k provides Nutanix AHV to ABLESTACK KVM migration
 command line tooling, manifest-based status tracking, and data
 transfer helpers.
